  "A condensed matter physicist models electron hopping on a 3-site lattice. The Hamiltonian is H = [[0,-t,0],[-t,0,-t],[0,-t,0]] where t=1. What is the characteristic polynomial of H?": "",
  "-lambda^3 - 2*lambda": "",
  "-lambda^3 + 3*lambda": "",
  "-lambda^3 + 2*lambda": "",
