  "(1/2)(|00><00| + |00><11| + |11><00| + |11><11|)": "",
  "(1/4)*I (the maximally mixed state)": "",
  "(1/2)(|01><01| + |10><10|)": "",
  "The GHZ state is |psi> = (1/sqrt(2))(|000> + |111>). Tracing out qubit 3: rho_12 = (1/2)(|00><00|*<0|0> + |00><11|*<0|1> + |11><00|*<1|0> + |11><11|*<1|1>) = (1/2)(|00><00| + |11><11|). The off-diagonal terms vanish because <0|1> = 0.": ""
